reviewText:
I cannot review for two reasons. 1. It is for a friend. 2. I do not speak Italian. However this area makes no allowance for this.
It says insufficient words, but this is because I have nothing to report. Of course I could remove it from my iPad but all that happens is it reappears! I keep writing in the hope that the number of words is enough to press submit and avoid we need more words turning up.
